require all of the access points

00:41:08.440 --> 00:41:11.020
at the children and
family to ensure

00:41:11.020 --> 00:41:15.500
that that child reaches
their optimal development.

00:41:15.500 --> 00:41:19.070
And so I think in terms
of pediatricians' offices,

00:41:19.070 --> 00:41:22.770
that's a primary place, but it's
up to all of us in the community

00:41:22.770 --> 00:41:29.230
in order to understand the
significant effect that traumas

00:41:29.230 --> 00:41:33.000
or other delays can have
on reading level and, thus,

00:41:33.000 --> 00:41:40.300
the future for that child and
even the future for society.

